reviewText: This is a fun video anyone who likes nostalgic tv ads.

A really nice collection of beer TV ads from the 50's and 60's (looks like mostly 50's) from a wide variety of brewers.  Lots of catchy jingles, retro animation and 50's -era sales pitches ("Yes, friends...").  Image quality of the ads is very good, no issue with deteriorated film.  Over an hour in length and the price is very reasonable.  Highly recommended.
